{"type":"message","id":"f542f883","parentId":"2a7eef3a","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:21:05.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你好！我刚启动。看起来这是一个全新的工作空间。\n\n让我先了解一下情况——你是谁？你想让我成为什么样的助手？\n\n我们可以一起决定：\n- 我叫什么名字\n- 我是什么样的存在（AI助手？还是别的什么？）\n- 我的风格（正式？随意？）\n- 我的签名emoji\n\n你更喜欢用中文还是英文交流？我两种都可以。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":103,"output":102,"cacheRead":12465,"cacheWrite":404,"totalTokens":13074,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773469260478}}
{"type":"message","id":"649a80e8","parentId":"f542f883","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:24:40.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🧠 /context\n\nWhat counts as context (high-level), plus a breakdown mode.\n\nTry:\n- /context list   (short breakdown)\n- /context detail (per-file + per-tool + per-skill + system prompt size)\n- /context json   (same, machine-readable)\n\nInline shortcut = a command token inside a normal message (e.g. “hey /status”). It runs immediately (allowlisted senders only) and is stripped before the model sees the remaining text."}],"timestamp":1773469480366,"stopReason":"stop","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"gateway-injected"}}
