{"type":"message","id":"ddb88a90","parentId":"39bb8b80","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:42:07.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"上下文窗口大小是由模型本身决定的，不是在 OpenClaw 里配置的。\n\n你现在用的模型是 `claude-sonnet-4-6`（Claude 3.5 Sonnet），它的上下文窗口是 **200K tokens**（约 15 万个中文字）。\n\n如果你想：\n\n**1. 换一个更大窗口的模型**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set model <model-name>\n```\n\n**2. 临时用不同模型**\n在对话里直接说 \"用 [模型名] 回答这个问题\"\n\n**3. 查看当前用量**\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n或者在对话里说 `/status`\n\n**4. 减少上下文消耗**\n- 清理 `MEMORY.md` 和 `memory/*.md` 里的旧内容\n- 精简 workspace 文件（`AGENTS.md`、`TOOLS.md` 等）\n- 开新会话（旧对话不会带过来）\n\n你是想解决什么问题？上下文不够用了，还是想优化 token 消耗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":111,"output":216,"cacheRead":12834,"cacheWrite":681,"totalTokens":13842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773470520750}}
