{"type":"message","id":"c4459835","parentId":"a7c94d50","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:52:43.477Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_PXdSVBT2mZCstBSZUFjB46","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Invalid config at /home/devbox/.openclaw/openclaw.json:\\n- channels.feishu2: unknown channel id: feishu2\n│\n◇  Config ───────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                            │\n│  Config invalid; doctor will run with best-effort config.  │\n│                                                            │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor changes ─────────────────────────────╮\n│                                              │\n│  feishu2 configured, enabled automatically.  │\n│                                              │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor warnings ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                       │\n│  - channels.feishu2.dmPolicy is \"allowlist\" but allowFrom is empty —  │\n│    all DMs will be blocked. Add sender IDs to                         │\n│    channels.feishu2.allowFrom, or run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to      │\n│    auto-migrate from pairing store when entries exist.                │\n│                                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig invalid\nFile: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nProblem:\n  - channels.feishu2: unknown channel id: feishu2\n\nRun: openclaw doctor --fix\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":3607,"aggregated":"Invalid config at /home/devbox/.openclaw/openclaw.json:\\n- channels.feishu2: unknown channel id: feishu2\n│\n◇  Config ───────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                            │\n│  Config invalid; doctor will run with best-effort config.  │\n│                                                            │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor changes ─────────────────────────────╮\n│                                              │\n│  feishu2 configured, enabled automatically.  │\n│                                              │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor warnings ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                       │\n│  - channels.feishu2.dmPolicy is \"allowlist\" but allowFrom is empty —  │\n│    all DMs will be blocked. Add sender IDs to                         │\n│    channels.feishu2.allowFrom, or run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to      │\n│    auto-migrate from pairing store when entries exist.                │\n│                                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig invalid\nFile: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nProblem:\n  - channels.feishu2: unknown channel id: feishu2\n\nRun: openclaw doctor --fix\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/home/devbox/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773471163470}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e1c425b","parentId":"c4459835","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:52:50.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我明白了，OpenClaw 的飞书插件可能不支持多个实例。让我先恢复配置，然后查看文档："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_R4shUs7r4BsRlfDtZyNQr5","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/openclaw.json","oldText":"  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"appId\": \"cli_a93e43ed3bf89bef\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"Tk4owhBr2dPo3r6MUPmhibM2gwVLmgye\",\n      \"domain\": \"feishu\",\n      \"connectionMode\": \"websocket\",\n      \"requireMention\": true,\n      \"dmPolicy\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"groupPolicy\": \"open\",\n      \"allowFrom\": [\n        \"ou_d3910e3b5e12b162c8bdae01eeab5c7b\"\n      ],\n      \"groupAllowFrom\": []\n    },\n    \"feishu2\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"appId\": \"cli_a93fb88c9a385cba\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"ZquVnKS8B49rtYwmKrCHSQpqJVF0kwef\",\n      \"domain\": \"feishu\",\n      \"connectionMode\": \"websocket\",\n      \"requireMention\": true,\n      \"dmPolicy\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"groupPolicy\": \"open\",\n      \"allowFrom\": [],\n      \"groupAllowFrom\": []\n    }\n  }","newText":"  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"appId\": \"cli_a93e43ed3bf89bef\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"Tk4owhBr2dPo3r6MUPmhibM2gwVLmgye\",\n      \"domain\": \"feishu\",\n      \"connectionMode\": \"websocket\",\n      \"requireMention\": true,\n      \"dmPolicy\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"groupPolicy\": \"open\",\n      \"allowFrom\": [\n        \"ou_d3910e3b5e12b162c8bdae01eeab5c7b\"\n      ],\n      \"groupAllowFrom\": []\n    }\n  }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":722,"output":464,"cacheRead":21550,"cacheWrite":1478,"totalTokens":24214,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773471163475}}
