{"type":"message","id":"7af4697f","parentId":"369490d9","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:53:21.015Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_JSdPCwoe6Xr0Ah0mumBBpF","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Doctor changes ─────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                              │\n│  Moved channels.feishu single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.feishu.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                              │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_get_user: Registered feishu_get_user tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_search_user: Registered feishu_search_user tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat_members: Registered feishu_chat_members tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat, feishu_chat_members[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_im_user_message: Registered feishu_im_user_message tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_im_user_fetch_resource: Registered feishu_im_user_fetch_resource tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_im: Registered feishu_im_user_message, feishu_im_user_fetch_resource, feishu_im_user_get_messages, feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages, feishu_im_user_search_messages[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_calendar_calendar: Registered feishu_calendar_calendar tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_calendar_event: Registered feishu_calendar_event tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_calendar_event_attendee: Registered feishu_calendar_event_attendee tool[39m\n[