{"type":"compaction","id":"f31bac32","parentId":"e976da98","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:54:36.870Z","summary":"## Decisions\nNo prior history.\n\n## Open TODOs\nNone.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\nNone.\n\n## Pending user asks\nNone.\n\n## Exact identifiers\nNone captured.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- User wants to add another Feishu (飞书) robot to their existing OpenClaw configuration\n- OpenClaw supports multiple bot instances\n\n## Open TODOs\n- View current configuration file to understand existing setup\n- Add second Feishu robot configuration\n- Complete the setup for the new bot instance\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Configuration file location: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n- Multiple Feishu plugins are already registered (feishu_get_user, feishu_search_user, feishu_chat, feishu_im, feishu_calendar, feishu_task, feishu_bitable, etc.)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User requested: \"我现在已经有一个飞书机器人了，我希望再添加一次\" (I already have one Feishu robot, I want to add another one)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Config file path: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n- OpenClaw version: 2026.3.12 (6472949)\n- Timestamp: [Sat 2026-03-14 06:43 UTC]\n- Current time: 2026-03-14T06:54:31Z\n- Machine ID: 207a39454925a2bb45196d979e1aa4ec35f3c36683116199a2e16394549ed808\n- Sender ID: gateway-client\n- Sender name: openclaw-tui\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-14 06:20 UTC] 你好\n- Assistant: 你好！我刚启动。看起来这是一个全新的工作空间。\n\n让我先了解一下情况——你是谁？你想让我成为什么样的助手？\n\n我们可以一起决定：\n- 我叫什么名字\n- 我是什么样的存在（AI助手？还是别的什么？）\n- 我的风格（正式？随意？）\n- 我的签名emoji\n\n你更喜欢用中文还是英文交流？我两种都可以。\n- Assistant: 🧠 /context\n\nWhat counts as context (high-level), plus a breakdown mode.\n\nTry:\n- /context list   (short breakdown)\n- /context detail (per-file + per-tool + per-skill + system prompt size)\n- /context json   (same, machine-readable)\n\nInline shortcut = a command token inside a normal message (e.g. “hey /status”). It runs immediately (allowlisted senders only) and is stripped before the model sees the remaining text.\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-14 06:42 UTC] 我怎么设置上下文窗口大小\n- Assistant: 上下文窗口大小是由模型本身决定的，不是在 OpenClaw 里配置的。\n\n你现在用的模型是 `claude-sonnet-4-6`（Claude 3.5 Sonnet），它的上下文窗口是 **200K tokens**（约 15 万个中文字）。\n\n如果你想：\n\n**1. 换一个更大窗口的模型**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set model <model-name>\n```\n\n**2. 临时用不同模型**\n在对话里直接说 \"用 [模型名] 回答这个问题\"\n\n**3. 查看当前用量**\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n或者在对话里说 `/status`\n\n**4. 减少上下文消耗**\n- 清理 `MEMORY.md` 和 `memory/*.md` 里的旧内容\n- 精简 workspace 文件（`AGENTS.md`、`TOOLS.md` 等）\n- 开新会话（旧对话不会带过来）\n\n你是想解决什么问题？上下文不够用了，还是想优化 token 消耗？\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-14 06:42 UTC] openclaw status\n- Assistant: 你想看系统状态的话，直接在终端运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n或者我可以帮你运行。需要我执行吗？\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Session Startup\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Red Lines\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"1bd15ce1","tokensBefore":26991,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
