{"type":"message","id":"22b5b335","parentId":"ea58af38","timestamp":"2026-03-14T07:30:48.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完整的 Lingzhu 鉴权 AK 是：\n\n```\nyfbixpor-7rhl-5ftf-gn4k-te37t6nbq5bk\n```\n\n**使用方式：**\n\n在灵珠平台配置时，使用 Bearer Token 认证：\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer yfbixpor-7rhl-5ftf-gn4k-te37t6nbq5bk\n```\n\n**SSE 端点：**\n```\nhttp://127.0.0.1:18789/metis/agent/api/sse\n```\n\n如果需要测试，可以运行：\n```bash\nopenclaw lingzhu curl\n```\n\n这会显示完整的 curl 调试示例。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":58,"output":118,"cacheRead":85098,"cacheWrite":12606,"totalTokens":97880,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773473441320}}
{"type":"message","id":"182b0884","parentId":"22b5b335","timestamp":"2026-03-14T08:10:34.036Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-14 08:10 UTC] 我希望能够访问 http://127.0.0.1:18789/metis/agent/api/sse 这个接口"}],"timestamp":1773475833993}}
{"type":"message","id":"72788f30","parentId":"182b0884","timestamp":"2026-03-14T08:10:42.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个接口已经配置好了，但目前只监听在 `127.0.0.1`（本地回环地址），只能从本机访问。\n\n如果你需要从外部访问，有几个方案：\n\n**方案 1：修改 Gateway 绑定地址（允许外部访问）**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set gateway.bind \"0.0.0.0\"\n```\n然后重启 Gateway。这样就可以通过服务器的 IP 地址访问了。\n\n**方案 2：使用反向代理（推荐，更安全）**\n用 nginx 或其他反向代理转发到 `127.0.0.1:18789`。\n\n**方案 3：SSH 隧道（临时测试）**\n```bash\nssh -L 18789:127.0.0.1:18789 user@your-server\n```\n\n**方案 4：Tailscale（如果已配置）**\nOpenClaw 支持 Tailscale，可以通过私有网络访问。\n\n你想用哪种方案？如果是在本机测试，现在就可以直接访问 `http://127.0.0.1:18789/metis/agent/api/sse`。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":124,"output":228,"cacheRead":85357,"cacheWrite":12640,"totalTokens":98349,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773475833997}}
{"type":"message","id":"aefea38d","parentId":"72788f30","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:20:39.670Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-14 10:20 UTC] Tailscale是什么，能解释下吗"}],"timestamp":1773483639664}}
{"type":"message","id":"d765fad2","parentId":"aefea38d","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:20:52.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tailscale 是一个基于 WireGuard 的零配置 VPN 服务，让你可以安全地连接分散在不同网络中的设备。\n\n**核心特点：**\n\n1. **零配置** - 不需要配置防火墙、端口转发或公网 IP\n2. **点对点加密** - 设备之间直接加密通信\n3. **私有网络** - 每个设备获得一个私有 IP（100.x.x.x），只有你授权的设备能访问\n4. **跨平台** - 支持 Linux、macOS、Windows、iOS、Android\n\n**使用场景：**\n\n- 远程访问家里/公司的服务器\n- 在咖啡厅安全访问内网服务\n- 多台设备之间组建私有网络\n- 替代传统 VPN，更简单更快\n\n**OpenClaw 集成：**\n\nOpenClaw 支持通过 Tailscale 暴露服务，这样你可以：\n- 从手机/其他设备安全访问 OpenClaw Gateway\n- 不需要公网 IP 或反向代理\n- 自动 HTTPS 加密\n\n**启用方式：**\n\n```bash\n# 1. 安装 Tailscale\ncurl -fsSL https://tailscale.com/install.sh | sh\n\n# 2. 登录\nsudo tailscale up\n\n# 3. 在 OpenClaw 中启用\nopenclaw config set gateway.tailscale.mode \"on\"\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n启用后，你会得到一个类似 `https://your-machine.tail-scale.ts.net` 的地址，可以从任何已加入你 Tailscale 网络的设备访问。\n\n你想启用 Tailscale 吗？还是用其他方案（比如改绑定地址或反向代理）？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":111,"output":358,"cacheRead":85713,"cacheWrite":12411,"totalTokens":98593,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773483639667}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8c598e7","parentId":"d765fad2","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:50:43.456Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-14 10:50 UTC] /skill"}],"timestamp":1773485443449}}
{"type":"message","id":"6bec592f","parentId":"a8c598e7","timestamp":"2026-03-14T10:50:51.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`/skill` 是一个命令，但我需要知道你想做什么。\n\n**常用的 skill 相关命令：**\n\n```bash\n# 列出所有 skills\nopenclaw skills list\n\n# 搜索 skills（从 ClawHub）\nnpx clawhub search <关键词>\n\n# 安装 skill\nnpx clawhub install <skill-name>\n\n# 查看某个 skill 的详情\nopenclaw skills info <skill-name>\n```\n\n你想：\n1. 查看已安装的 skills？\n2. 搜索新的 skills？\n3. 安装特定的 skill？\n4. 还是其他操作？\n\n告诉我具体需求，我来帮你。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":104,"output":137,"cacheRead":86199,"cacheWrite":13261,"totalTokens":99701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773485443453}}
