{"type":"message","id":"5302cb42","parentId":"237ac96e","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:42:41.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **OpenClaw with Apple** 已成功安装，状态显示 `ready`！\n\n**功能包括：**\n- 🍎 Apple iCloud 全功能访问（日历、提醒事项、备忘录）\n- 💪 Apple Health 深度健康分析\n- 🔄 双向待办同步（AI → iPhone 提醒事项/备忘录）\n\n**下一步需要配置 iCloud 账号。** 你需要运行：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/apple-icloud/scripts/icloud_auth.py\n```\n\n输入你的 Apple ID 和密码完成认证。需要我帮你继续配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":160,"output":147,"cacheRead":91515,"cacheWrite":13540,"totalTokens":105362,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773495752149}}
