{"type":"message","id":"d4e6d397","parentId":"3344fdba","timestamp":"2026-03-14T21:59:15.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的！根据你提供的步骤，让我检查已完成的进度：\n\n**✅ 已完成的步骤：**\n\n1. ✅ **Lingzhu Skill 已安装** - 插件在 `~/.openclaw/extensions/lingzhu`\n2. ✅ **鉴权 AK 已生成** - `yfbixpor-7rhl-5ftf-gn4k-te37t6nbq5bk`\n3. ✅ **聊天补全节点已开启** - `gateway.http.endpoints.chatCompletions.enabled: true`\n\n**📋 下一步需要做的：**\n\n**步骤 1：获取公网访问地址**\n\n你的服务现在监听在 `127.0.0.1:18789`，需要公网 IP 或域名才能让灵珠平台访问。有几个选项：\n\n1. **如果有公网 IP**：\n   - SSE 端点：`http://你的公网IP:18789/metis/agent/api/sse`\n   - 鉴权 AK：`yfbixpor-7rhl-5ftf-gn4k-te37t6nbq5bk`\n\n2. **如果没有公网 IP，需要内网穿透**：\n   - Cloudflare Tunnel（推荐）\n   - frp\n   - ngrok\n\n**步骤 2：在灵珠平台配置**\n\n1. 登录灵珠平台 → 创建智能体 → 三方智能体 → 自定义智能体\n2. 填入 URL：`http://你的公网地址:18789/metis/agent/api/sse`\n3. 填入 AK：`yfbixpor-7rhl-5ftf-gn4k-te37t6nbq5bk`\n4. 入参类型选择：文字\n5. **不要点击提审**\n\n**步骤 3：测试**\n\n在 RokidAI App → 设置 → 开发者 → 智能体调试 → 测试\n\n---\n\n**你现在需要决定：**\n1. 你有公网 IP 吗？\n2. 还是需要我帮你配置内网穿透（比如 Cloudflare Tunnel）？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":83,"output":371,"cacheRead":122472,"cacheWrite":19009,"totalTokens":141935,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773525542661}}
