{"type":"message","id":"5448d54f","parentId":"3f6a593c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:01:27.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"飞书功能是通过 `openclaw-lark` 插件提供的。由于我现在在 TUI 会话中，没有直接访问飞书工具的权限。\n\n**最简单的方法是：**\n\n你在飞书里给我发个消息（任意内容），然后我就可以在那个飞书会话里直接回复图片给你。\n\n或者，我可以把图片传到你的 Windows 机器上，你想用哪种方式？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":148,"output":97,"cacheRead":142521,"cacheWrite":20964,"totalTokens":163730,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773543678759}}
{"type":"message","id":"417c0c1f","parentId":"5448d54f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:06:10.640Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-15 11:04:23 GMT+8] Node: Thomas的MacBook Air (192.168.66.134) · app 2026.3.12 (2026031290) · mode remote · reason connect\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-15 11:06 GMT+8] 我已经为这个openclaw配置过飞书机器人了。也有对应的id。有什么方法能实现直接发送到飞书吗"}],"timestamp":1773543970602}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8876e54","parentId":"417c0c1f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:06:25.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"是的！既然你已经配置了飞书机器人，我可以直接通过飞书 API 发送图片。让我试试："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_y2Vp81fAI6DQPOxZ3PU7Co","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/send_feishu_image.py << 'EOF'\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport requests\nimport json\nimport sys\n\n# 飞书配置\nuser_id = \"ou_d3910e3b5e12b162c8bdae01eeab5c7b\"\nimage_path = \"/tmp/test-cat.png\"\n\n# 从 OpenClaw 配置读取\nimport os\nconfig_path = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\")\nwith open(config_path) as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 获取第一个飞书账号的配置\nfeishu_config = config[\"channels\"][\"feishu\"][\"accounts\"][\"main\"]\napp_id = feishu_config[\"appId\"]\napp_secret = feishu_config[\"appSecret\"]\n\n# 获取 tenant_access_token\ntoken_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\"\ntoken_resp = requests.post(token_url, json={\n    \"app_id\": app_id,\n    \"app_secret\": app_secret\n})\ntoken_data = token_resp.json()\nif token_data.get(\"code\") != 0:\n    print(f\"获取 token 失败: {token_data}\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\naccess_token = token_data[\"tenant_access_token\"]\n\n# 上传图片\nupload_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/images\"\nwith open(image_path, \"rb\") as f:\n    files = {\"image\": f}\n    data = {\"image_type\": \"message\"}\n    headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {access_token}\"}\n    upload_resp = requests.post(upload_url, headers=headers, data=data, files=files)\n\nupload_data = upload_resp.json()\nif upload_data.get(\"code\") != 0:\n    print(f\"上传图片失败: {upload_data}\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nimage_key = upload_data[\"data\"][\"image_key\"]\nprint(f\"图片上传成功: {image_key}\")\n\n# 发送消息\nsend_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages\"\nparams = {\"receive_id_type\": \"open_id\"}\nmessage_content = {\n    \"image_key\": image_key\n}\npayload = {\n    \"receive_id\": user_id,\n    \"msg_type\": \"image\",\n    \"content\": json.dumps(message_content)\n}\n\nsend_resp = requests.post(send_url, headers=headers, params=params, json=payload)\nsend_data = send_resp.json()\n\nif send_data.get(\"code\") == 0:\n    print(\"图片发送成功！\")\nelse:\n    print(f\"发送失败: {send_data}\")\nEOF\npython3 /tmp/send_feishu_image.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-right-codes","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":178,"output":690,"cacheRead":136066,"cacheWrite":22100,"totalTokens":159034,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773543970612}}
